-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-11/spain-s-mato-says-patients-may-pay-more-for-drugs-el-mundo-says.html
The Spanish government is
considering increasing patients’ contribution to drug bills
depending on their income,  El Mundo  reported, citing comments by
Health Minister Ana Mato.  To contact the reporter on this story:
